{{page-title "About"}}

<div class="about-container">
  <h2>About This Project</h2>
  
  <section class="about-section">
    <h3>🎯 Purpose</h3>
    <p>
      This project demonstrates microfrontend architecture using Ember as the host
      application and React as the microfrontend. It mirrors the architecture used
      in Freshservice's production application.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h3>🏗️ Architecture</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Ruby on Rails 7 (API mode)</li>
      <li><strong>Host App:</strong> Ember.js 5 (Octane edition)</li>
      <li><strong>Microfrontend:</strong> React 18 with Vite</li>
      <li><strong>UI Library:</strong> Custom React component library</li>
      <li><strong>Integration:</strong> Webpack Module Federation</li>
      <li><strong>Communication:</strong> MessageChannel API</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h3>🚀 Integration Patterns</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Full Ember Page:</strong> Dashboard (traditional Ember)</li>
      <li><strong>Hybrid Page:</strong> Users (Ember + embedded React component)</li>
      <li><strong>Full React MFE:</strong> Tickets (React handles everything)</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

